## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6254">Номер банковского счета для Израиль</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6254">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6255">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6255">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6256">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6256">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6257">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6257">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6258">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6258">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6259">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6259">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6260">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6260">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6261">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6261">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6262">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6262">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6263">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6263">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6264">Неформатированные:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6264">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6265">	13 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6265">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6266">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6266">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6267">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6267">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6268">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6268">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6269">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6269">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6270">регулярное выражение Regex_israel_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6270">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6271">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_israel_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6271">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6272">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6272">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6273">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6273">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6274">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6274">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6275">Bank Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6275">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6276">Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6276">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6277">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6277">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6278">Национальный идентификационный номер для Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6278">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6279">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6279">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6280">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6280">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6281">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6281">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6282">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6282">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6283">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6283">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6284">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6284">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6285">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6285">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6286">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6286">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6287">функция Func_israeli_national_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6287">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6288">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Israel_National_ID;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6288">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6289">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6289">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6308">Номер водительского удостоверения для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6308">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6309">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6309">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6310">сочетание 10 букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6310">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6311">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6311">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6312">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6312">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6313">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6313">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6314">буква "A" или "V" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6314">the letter "A" or "V" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6315">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6315">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6316">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6316">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6317">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6317">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6318">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6318">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6319">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6319">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6320">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6320">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6321">регулярное выражение Regex_italy_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6321">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6322">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6322">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6323">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6323">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6324">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6324">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6325">numero di patente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6325">numero di patente</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6326">patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6326">patente di guida</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6327">patente guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6327">patente guida</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6328">patenti di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6328">patenti di guida</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6329">patenti guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6329">patenti guida</span></span>

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6330">Финансовый код Для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6330">Italy fiscal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6331">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6331">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6332">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6332">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6333">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6333">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6334">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6334">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6335">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6335">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6336">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6336">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6337">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6337">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6338">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6338">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6339">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6339">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6340">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6340">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6341">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем consonants в имени семейства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6341">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6342">три буквы, соответствующие первому, третьему и четвертому consonants в первом имени</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6342">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6343">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6343">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6344">одна буква, соответствующая букве месяца рождения, — буквы используются в алфавитном порядке, но используются только буквы A к E, H, L, M, P, R to T (таким образом, январь A, а октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6344">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (thus, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6345">две цифры, соответствующие дню месяца рождения, чтобы различать полы, 40 добавляется в день рождения для</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6345">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6346">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду региона, относя к замурованию человека (коды для разных стран используются для внешних стран)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6346">four digits that corresponds to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6347">одна цифра четности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6347">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6348">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6348">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6349">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6349">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6350">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6350">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6351">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6351">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6352">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6352">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6353">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6353">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6354">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6354">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6355">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6355">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6390">Номер паспорта гражданина Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6390">Italy passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6391">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6391">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6392">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6392">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6393">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6393">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6394">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6394">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6395">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6395">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6396">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6396">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6397">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6397">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6398">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6398">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6399">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6399">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6400">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6400">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6401">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6401">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6402">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6402">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6403">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6403">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6424">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6424">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6425">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6425">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6426">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6426">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6427">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6427">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6428">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6428">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6429">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6429">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6430">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6430">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6431">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6431">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6432">13-символьный буквонумерный шаблон с необязательными делетерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6432">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6433">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6433">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6434">13 символов букв и цифр с необязательными делетерами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6434">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6435">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6435">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6436">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6436">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6437">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6437">optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6438">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6438">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6439">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6439">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6440">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6440">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6441">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6441">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6442">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6442">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6443">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6443">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6444">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6444">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6445">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6445">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6446">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6446">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6448">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6448">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6454">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6454">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6455">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6456">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6456">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6457">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6458">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6458">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6459">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6459">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6460">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6460">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6461">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6461">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6462">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6462">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6463">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6463">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6464">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6464">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6465">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6465">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6466">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6466">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6467">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6467">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6468">Функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6468">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6469">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6469">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6470">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6470">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6471">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6471">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6472">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6472">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6473">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6473">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6474">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6474">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6475">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6475">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6476">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6476">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_bank_account"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6477">Keyword_jp_bank_account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6477">Keyword_jp_bank_account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6478">Checking Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6478">Checking Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6479">Checking Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6479">Checking Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6480">Checking Account #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6480">Checking Account #</span></span>

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6522">Номер водительского удостоверения для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6522">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6523">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6523">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6524">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6524">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6525">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6525">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6526">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6526">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6527">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6527">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6528">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6528">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6529">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6529">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6530">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6530">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6531">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6531">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6532">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6532">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6570">Мой номер для Японии — корпоративный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6570">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6571">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6571">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6572">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6572">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6573">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6573">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6574">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6574">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6575">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6575">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6576">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6576">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6577">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6577">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6578">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6578">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6579">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6579">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6580">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6580">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6581">одна цифра от одной до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6581">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6582">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6582">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6583">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6583">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6584">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6584">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6585">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6585">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6586">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6586">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6587">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6587">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6588">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6588">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6589">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6589">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6590">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6590">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6591">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6591">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6592">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6592">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6593">корпоративный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6593">corporate number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6594">マイナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6594">マイナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6595">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6595">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6596">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6596">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6597">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6597">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6603">Мой номер для Японии — личный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6603">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6604">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6604">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6605">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6605">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6606">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6606">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6607">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6607">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6608">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6608">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6609">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6609">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6610">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6610">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6611">12-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6611">12 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6612">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6612">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6613">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6613">12 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6614">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6614">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6615">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6615">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6616">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6616">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6617">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6617">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6618">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6618">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6619">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6619">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6620">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6620">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6621">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6621">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6622">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6622">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6623">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6623">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6624">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6624">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6625">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6625">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6626">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6626">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6628">Keyword_japan_my_number_personal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6628">Keyword_japan_my_number_personal</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6631">個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6631">個人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6632">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6632">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6633">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6633">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6634">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6634">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6635">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6635">個人番号カード</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6637">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6637">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>

## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6639">Номер паспорта гражданина Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6639">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6640">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6640">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6641">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6641">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6642">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6642">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6643">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6643">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6644">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6644">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6645">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6645">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6646">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6646">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6647">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6647">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6648">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6648">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6649">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6649">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6666">Номер карты для проживания в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6666">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6667">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6667">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6668">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6668">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6669">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6669">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6670">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6670">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6671">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6671">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6672">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6672">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6673">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6673">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6674">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6674">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6675">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6675">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6676">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6676">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6677">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6677">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6678">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6678">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6679">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6679">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6680">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6680">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6681">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6681">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6682">Номер карты для проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6682">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6683">Карты проживания нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6683">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6684">Карточка для проживания #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6684">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6685">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6685">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6686">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6686">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6687">在留番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6687">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6688">Номер регистрации резидента Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6688">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6689">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6689">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6690">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6690">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6691">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6691">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6692">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6692">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6693">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6693">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6694">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6694">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6695">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6695">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6696">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6696">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6697">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6697">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6698">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6698">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6711">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6711">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6712">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6712">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6713">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6713">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6714">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6714">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6715">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6715">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6716">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6716">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6717">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6717">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6718">шесть цифр ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6718">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6719">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6719">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6720">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6720">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6721">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6721">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6722">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6722">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6723">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6723">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6724">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6724">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6725">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6725">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6726">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6726">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6727">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6727">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6728">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6728">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6749">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6749">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6750">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6750">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6751">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6751">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6752">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6752">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6753">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6753">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6754">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6754">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6755">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6755">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6756">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6756">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6757">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6757">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6758">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6758">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6759">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6759">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6760">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6760">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6761">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6761">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6886">Персональный код для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6886">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6887">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6887">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6888">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6888">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6889">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6889">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6890">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6890">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6891">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6891">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6892">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6892">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6893">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6893">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6894">одна цифра, соответствующая годовщине рождения ("0" для 19-го, "1" для 20-го и "2" для 21-го)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6894">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6895">четыре цифры, генерируемые случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6895">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6896">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6896">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6897">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6897">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6898">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6898">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6899">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6899">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6900">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6900">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6901">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6901">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6902">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6902">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6903">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6903">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6904">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6904">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6905">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6905">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6906">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6906">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6907">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6907">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6970">Номер паспорта гражданина Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6970">Latvia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6971">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6971">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6972">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6972">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6973">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6973">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6974">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6974">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6975">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6975">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6976">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6976">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6977">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6977">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6978">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6978">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6979">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6979">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6980">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6980">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6981">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6981">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6982">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6982">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-6983">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-6983">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-7003">Номер водительского удостоверения для Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-7003">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-7004">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-7004">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-7005">восемь цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-7005">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-7006">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-7006">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-7007">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-7007">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-7008">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-7008">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-7009">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-7009">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7ab61-7010">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-7010">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7ab61-7011">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-7011">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-7012">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-7012">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7ab61-7013">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ab61-7013">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
